               HammerDB 
               
               HammerDB
                  is an open source database load testing and benchmarking tool
                  for Oracle Database, Microsoft SQL Server, IBM DB2, TimesTen,
                  MySQL, MariaDB,   PostgreSQL,
                   Postgres
                  Plus Advanced Server,  Greenplum,
                   Redis,
                  Amazon Aurora and Redshift and Trafodion SQL on Hadoop  
               
                   
               
               
        
                         
                 
               
                 
